This is a placeholder ZIP file for the PvP Kraft texture pack.

To turn this into a working Minecraft Bedrock resource pack:
1. Extract this ZIP (or just keep it Zipped).
2. Ensure it contains:
   - manifest.json (The unique ID and version of your pack)
   - pack_icon.png (The 64x64 or 128x128 image users see in settings)
   - textures/items/ (Contains your short sword, gapples, etc.)
   - textures/blocks/ (Contains your clean cobwebs)
3. Rename the extension from .zip to .mcpack if you want it to auto-install in Minecraft.

Happy building!
